title: 'Danny Dyer sent me pictures of his manhood', fan claims | Daily Mail Online
text: Young mother says married EastEnders star Danny Dyer sent her pictures of his manhood in a series of lewd messages amid reports of a meltdown The EastEnders star allegedly sent her a series of late night flirty messages These culminated in him sending a picture of his penis sticking out of his boxers He was due to marry the mother of his children Joanne Mas nine weeks later Dyer has cheated on Ms Mas several times in the past but has been taken back The 39-year-old is currently on a break from the soap amid rumours about his private life
